::Zardus/DevilDuer/Prowl::

Zardus nods. "Very well. Follow me, the CR chambers are this way."

Zardus walks off toward the CR chambers. He raises his commlink to 
his mouth. "Devil, anything with Wolfgang?"

"He tried to escape. I shot him. He hasn't done anything else, 
though." DevilDuer's voice replies.

Zardus nods and keeps walking toward the CR chambers.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Prowl puts Iron Raptor in a CR chamber. He looks at her for a second 
before closing the door. The CR chamber activates.
